Packages

    apt-get install nginx

Version

    1.4.6

In /etc/nginx/nginx.conf uncomment

    server_names_hash_bucket_size 64;

In /etc/nginx/nginx.conf, into http block, add the following line

    include uwsgi_params;

Create symbolic links

    sudo ln -s /home/xleo/src/lvidarte/django-calcifer-apps/conf/nginx/calcifer.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/calcifer.conf

Restart nginx

    service nginx restart
